      • toStream

        public static <T> java.util.stream.Stream<T> toStream(Optional<T> optional)
        Returns a singleton stream of an Optional's value if present, otherwise an empty stream. Useful for filtering present instances in a stream pipeline: 
        
 Stream.of(Optional.empty(), Optional.of(1), Optional.of(2))
   .flatMap(Optionals::toStream)

 // Yields a stream of 2 elements, [1, 2]
